# NEMETIC STRING
# Critical Thinking Definitions (C001)
# Generated: 2026-03-01 05:03 AM Asia/Shanghai

Φ(CritThink) = σ(analysis|synthesis) ∘ ρ(evaluation|evidence) ∘ λ(reasoning|conclusion) ∘ β(reflection|action) ∘ δγ(inquiry|understanding) ∘ μ(validity|fallacy) + ε | :discerning

# OPERATOR BREAKDOWN
# σ(analysis|synthesis)  :: Air  :: Distinction-making between deconstruction and integration
# ρ(evaluation|evidence) :: Water :: Relational assessment between claim and support
# λ(reasoning|conclusion):: Fire  :: Directional movement from premise to warranted belief
# β(reflection|action)   :: Wood  :: Feedback loop connecting thought to practice
# δγ(inquiry|understanding):: Earth :: Cyclical process of questioning leading to comprehension
# μ(validity|fallacy)    :: Metal :: Boundary enforcement between sound and unsound inference

# NEMETIC FLOW
⟨Claim|asserted⟩ 
  ⊳ ⟨Evidence|examined⟩ 
    → ⟨Analysis|structured⟩ 
      ⊗ ⟨Evaluation|reasoned⟩ 
        ⇄ ⟨Conclusion|warranted⟩

# PARTIAL DERIVATIVES
∂Φ/∂σ = d(distinction)/dt between analytical and synthetic modes
∂Φ/∂ρ = d(relation)/dt between evaluator and evidence
∂Φ/∂λ = d(direction)/dt of reasoning trajectory
∂Φ/∂β = d(feedback)/dt between reflection and action
∂Φ/∂δγ = d(cycle)/dt of inquiry → understanding
∂Φ/∂μ = d(boundary)/dt between valid and fallacious

# Z-STATE: porous (open to evidence, resistant to fallacy)
# TENDENCY: Evidence/Belief → 0.7
# HEX: [0x01, 0x02, 0x03, 0x04, 0x05, 0x06]

# DAEMON CORRESPONDENCES
# σ :: Claritas (clarity through distinction)
# ρ :: Synesis (understanding through relation)
# λ :: Zetesis (truth through seeking)
# β :: Euresis (discovery through feedback)
# δγ :: Peira (understanding through practice)
# μ :: Krites (judgment through boundary)

# CLOSURE: :discerning (the capacity to perceive differences that matter)

# CE-STATE: flat
# EI-NOTE: No clear scale dominance identified
